{
  "id": "sys-09-internal-reporting-dashboard",
  "name": "SYS 07 — Internal Reporting Dashboard",
  "description": "Triggered by deal stage change webhook, contact change webhook, or every 4 hours. Pushes HubSpot pipeline and contact data into the master Google Sheet (Pipeline, Contacts, Revenue tabs) so Looker Studio or other dashboards stay up to date. Single source for internal reporting.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## SYS 07 — Internal Reporting Dashboard\n\n**Triggers:** (1) Webhook when deal stage changes, (2) Webhook when contact changes, (3) Every 4 hours (cron).\n\n**What it does:** Pushes HubSpot pipeline and contact data into the master Google Sheet (Pipeline, Contacts, Revenue, etc.) so Looker Studio or other dashboards stay up to date. Formats deal/contact rows and appends or updates the relevant tabs. Single source for internal reporting.\n\n**Dependencies:** CONFIG, HubSpot, Google Sheets. Dashboard connects to the same sheet.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "note-sys09",
      "name": "Note — About this workflow",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1.3,
      "position": [
        80,
        80
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "hubspot-deal-stage-change",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "options": {}
